Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:59.20,script,,0,0,0,,The conference members are basically selected after we do a strict examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:03.70,script,,0,0,0,,There really aren't any suspicious people, so to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.10,script,,0,0,0,,or any people with problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:09.40,script,,0,0,0,,If there are any conflicts between two members,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.40,script,,0,0,0,,we'll take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:14.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a job I just chose to do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:20.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because employment opportunities were limited for a third-class university graduate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or so I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:28.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or I was trying to make myself think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In truth, I wanted to experience people's happiness,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to experience people's sadness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:44.50,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to place myself somewhere where people encounter and separate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:56.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I kept doing that, I thought I'd be able to do the same someday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:10.30,script,,0,0,0,,From now on, I want you to help me with the house chores more often than before, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:17.30,script,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of bad doing this to you since there's such a large age difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.70,script,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You don't seem too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.70,script,,0,0,0,,You're finally going to be a big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.10,script,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't it almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.60,script,,0,0,0,,One more month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.80,script,,0,0,0,,You're a big brother now, aren't you, Ko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.30,script,,0,0,0,,Yes! We did it, Koshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.70,script,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:04.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a kind of a happy, yet scary, feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:11.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that was the only time I had that feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.60,script,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.80,script,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.70,script,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.20,script,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.70,script,,0,0,0,,My, my, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:20.50,script,,0,0,0,,Come on, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.30,script,,0,0,0,,Ugh... Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.70,script,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't cry, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.40,script,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.40,script,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.40,script,,0,0,0,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:24.00,script,,0,0,0,,You aren't bullying her while we're out, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.10,script,,0,0,0,,Nanoka seems to be afraid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.60,script,,0,0,0,,Who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.50,script,,0,0,0,,You're so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.00,script,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.80,script,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:01.30,script,,0,0,0,,Will you come to the other room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.90,script,,0,0,0,,It's not that we're quarreling with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.90,script,,0,0,0,,or we got into a big fight or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.20,script,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:25.30,script,,0,0,0,,We thought we should live separately before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.90,script,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.70,script,,0,0,0,,We're sorry that we have to make you go through the sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.60,script,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.90,script,,0,0,0,,Even though we'll be living apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.50,script,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean I'll stop being your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:40.10,script,,0,0,0,,or that she's no longer your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.10,script,,0,0,0,,We're still family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.10,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:56.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought divorces weren't such peaceful things in my mind as a child, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:03.60,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could tell that mom and dad were trying to separate peacefully for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.40,script,,0,0,0,,Well, we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:19.30,script,,0,0,0,,Koshiro, keep an eye on the house for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.40,script,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.00,script,,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:31.60,script,,0,0,0,,Don't look so sulky forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.40,script,,0,0,0,,Be more honest with yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.50,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.20,script,,0,0,0,,You can come any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.30,script,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.30,script,,0,0,0,,What, you've been going home early lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.10,script,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:12.00,script,,0,0,0,,He must want to see Nanoka-san as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:14.00,script,,0,0,0,,I'm so envious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.70,script,,0,0,0,,No way. He's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you, brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:55.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is it that I even headed there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.70,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without even understanding it myself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:12.10,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was walking in the town that she grew up in without me knowing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.50,script,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.20,script,,0,0,0,,So you finally came to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.40,script,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.80,script,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.20,script,,0,0,0,,It's you, Koshiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.30,script,,0,0,0,,I thought you would've forgotten my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.30,script,,0,0,0,,Did you forget my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:50.70,script,,0,0,0,,See? Even if we haven't seen each other for years, that's how it is between a  parent and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.20,script,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.50,script,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.70,script,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.90,script,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:04.20,script,,0,0,0,,You just suddenly came. There must be some reason, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.10,script,,0,0,0,,No reason. I just felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.10,script,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.70,script,,0,0,0,,From when she was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.60,script,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.20,script,,0,0,0,,She just loves bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:53.10,script,,0,0,0,,She really is your younger sister, that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.00,script,,0,0,0,,You exchanged dolls, I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:04.40,script,,0,0,0,,Nanoka was talking about it so happily when she came back during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.70,script,,0,0,0,,Why did you send her over to our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.70,script,,0,0,0,,When you took her with you when you got divorced,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.40,script,,0,0,0,,why would you suddenly bring her back to dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.80,script,,0,0,0,,Because she got into a high school near your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.10,script,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:25.70,script,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad if she had to commute two hours each way every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.80,script,,0,0,0,,What? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.90,script,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:39.40,script,,0,0,0,,What? did you come all the way over just to sulk?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.50,script,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.30,script,,0,0,0,,Here, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.80,script,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.70,script,,0,0,0,,How many years has it been since I last cut your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.90,script,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:10.60,script,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't let me cut much after you became a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.60,script,,0,0,0,,What were you getting all worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.20,script,,0,0,0,,Big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.50,script,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.40,script,,0,0,0,,She isn't bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.60,script,,0,0,0,,Saying, big brother, big brother, big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.80,script,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.10,script,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.50,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what my brother is like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.20,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to meet him soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if he'll help me with studying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.40,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, nothing, nothing at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:48.80,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He will help you, I'm sure, with your studies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.90,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:14:01.80,script,,0,0,0,,She probably really wanted to live with you guys... or just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:03.60,script,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.40,script,,0,0,0,,So take good care of her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.90,script,,0,0,0,,Zenzou-san is no good when you really need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.10,script,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:16.90,script,,0,0,0,,What? You better have a more firm character.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.60,script,,0,0,0,,You're a big brother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.60,script,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.70,script,,0,0,0,,What would you do if I made her unhappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.90,script,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.80,script,,0,0,0,,If I somehow made her unhappy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.30,script,,0,0,0,,what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.20,script,,0,0,0,,If such a thing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.60,script,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't let you off with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.40,script,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.00,script,,0,0,0,,Odd child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.00,script,,0,0,0,,You still don't seem to be very honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.10,script,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.90,script,,0,0,0,,It means you haven't grown up at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.00,script,,0,0,0,,You'd better be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.80,script,,0,0,0,,It's the most difficult phase
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.60,script,,0,0,0,,at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.90,script,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay a little longer, since its been a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.20,script,,0,0,0,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.80,script,,0,0,0,,I have work tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.80,script,,0,0,0,,You have to eat properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.60,script,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.50,script,,0,0,0,,Oh yes. Nanoka's flavoring is usually a little too strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.60,script,,0,0,0,,so tell her to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.60,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:46.00,script,,0,0,0,,And don't give her too much allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.40,script,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't give her any even if she begged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.10,script,,0,0,0,,And tell her not to stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.70,script,,0,0,0,,I got it already. I'll be late for my train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.60,script,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.50,script,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.20,script,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.90,script,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:08.10,script,,0,0,0,,Okay, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.90,script,,0,0,0,,Get along well as siblings, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.90,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.90,script,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.20,script,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.10,script,,0,0,0,,I'm... home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.30,script,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.70,script,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.60,script,,0,0,0,,You're not going to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.60,script,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.50,script,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:19.70,script,,0,0,0,,Hey, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.00,script,,0,0,0,,Where did you go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.70,script,,0,0,0,,Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.40,script,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.50,script,,0,0,0,,Just for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.00,script,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.50,script,,0,0,0,,Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.90,script,,0,0,0,,You should've taken me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.10,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fine with being big brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Siblings that get along well is fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:54.50,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the role that I was given,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.60,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do what I must.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:00.00,script,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:03.30,script,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to get up early tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.00,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.50,script,,0,0,0,,But you too, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.10,script,,0,0,0,,I'll take a smoke and then go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.20,script,,0,0,0,,So go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.00,script,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.40,script,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.30,script,,0,0,0,,Good night then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.20,script,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
